    • 方法详细资料

      • getUxRestrictions

        public CarUxRestrictions getUxRestrictions(int drivingState,
                                           float currentSpeed)
        Returns the restrictions for CarUxRestrictionsManager.UX_RESTRICTION_MODE_BASELINE based on current driving state.
        参数:
        drivingState - Driving state. See values in CarDrivingStateEvent.CarDrivingState.
        currentSpeed - Current speed in meter per second.

      • getUxRestrictions

        public CarUxRestrictions getUxRestrictions(int drivingState,
                                           float currentSpeed,
                                           java.lang.String mode)
        Returns the restrictions based on current driving state and restriction mode.

        Restriction mode allows a different set of restrictions to be applied in the same driving state.

        参数:
        drivingState - Driving state. See values in CarDrivingStateEvent.CarDrivingState.
        currentSpeed - Current speed in meter per second.
        mode - Current UX Restriction mode.

      • getPhysicalPort

        public java.lang.Integer getPhysicalPort()
        Returns the port this configuration applies to. When port is not set, the combination of occupant zone id getOccupantZoneId() and display type getDisplayType() can also identify a display. If neither port nor occupant zone id and display type are set, the configuration will apply to default display android.view.Display#DEFAULT_DISPLAY.

        Returns null if port is not set.

      • getOccupantZoneId

        public int getOccupantZoneId()
        Returns the id of the occupant zone of the display this configuration applies to.

        Occupant zone id and display type getDisplayType() should both exist to identity a display. When occupant zone id and display type getDisplayType() are not set, port getPhysicalPort() can also identify a display.

        If neither port nor occupant zone id and display type are set, the configuration will apply to default display android.view.Display#DEFAULT_DISPLAY.

        返回:
        the occupant zone id or CarOccupantZoneManager.OccupantZoneInfo.INVALID_ZONE_ID if the occupant zone id is not set.

      • getDisplayType

        public int getDisplayType()
        Returns the type of the display in occupant zone identified by getOccupantZoneId() this configuration applies to.

        Occupant zone id getOccupantZoneId() and display type should both exist to identity a display. When display type and occupant zone id getOccupantZoneId() are not set, port getPhysicalPort() can also identify a display.

        If neither port nor occupant zone id and display type are set, the configuration will apply to default display android.view.Display#DEFAULT_DISPLAY.

        返回:
        the display type or CarOccupantZoneManager.DISPLAY_TYPE_UNKNOWN if the display type is not set.
